---
title: Hungarian-Inspired Turkey Paprikash with Noodles and Crispy Shallots
description: This dish will have you dreaming of Oma's paprikash. Creamy, sauce-smothered, paprika-spiced turkey and sweet roasted peppers are piled on top of buttered noodles.
